title: Land of Osiris and the Giza Power Plant
description:
Stephen Mehler and Christopher Dunn speaking about their findings and interpretations of Egyptian Archeology, and more over the uncovering of an Ancient Egyptian Oral tradition that depicts a pre Egyptian culture going back possibly 65,000 years.  They explain the cyclic patterns of civilization and the continuous rise and fall of man and his technology.  

We are not the pinnacle of civilization that we think we are!

Enjoy!!!

~ Flforce
